ttp://iyiparti.org.tr/baskanlik-divani]</ref>\n\n=== Parliamentary Group Leader ===\n\n* [[Orhan \u00c7ak\u0131rlar]]<ref name=\"Parliamentary Leader\">https://www.tbmm.gov.tr/develop/owa/milletvekillerimiz_sd.bilgi?p_donem=27&p_sicil=7575</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://iyiparti.org.tr/}}\n\n{{Turkish nationalism}}\n{{Turkish political parties}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:\u0130yi Party}}\n[[Category:\u0130yi Party|*]]\n[[Category:2017 establishments in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Conservative parties in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Nationalist parties in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Political parties established in 2017]]\n[[Category:Political parties in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Secularism in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Pro-European political parties in Turkey]]\n", "text_old": "{{about |the Turkish political party|the South African political party|Good (political party)|}}\n\n{{short description|nationalist political party in Turkey}}\n\n{{Infobox political party\n| name = Good Party\n| logo = Logo of the Good Party.svg\n| colorcode = #42ABE2\n| foundation = {{start date|2017|10|25|df=y}}\n| ideology = {{nowrap|[[Liberal conservatism]]<ref>https://www.speakfreely.today/2017/12/06/just-good-good-party/</ref><br>[[Turkish nationalism]]<ref name=dw>{{cite news|title=Turkish nationalists form new party challenging Erdogan|url=http://www.dw.com/en/turkish-nationalists-form-new-party-challenging-erdogan/a-41101708|work=Deutsche Welle|date=25 October 2017}}</ref><br>[[Development economics|Economic developmentalism]]<ref>https://www.haberturk.com/iyi-parti-genel-baskani-meral-aksener-den-onemli-aciklamalar-2553314</ref><br>[[Kemalism]]<ref name=dw/><ref name=\"Nordsieck\"/><br>[[Social justice]]<ref name=\"social justice\">http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/meral-aksener-halk-parlamenter-sistemi-istiyor-1713914</ref><br>[[Civic nationalism]]<ref name=\"haberturk.com\">{{cite web|url=http://www.haberturk.com/gundem/haber/1602198-yusuf-halacoglu-yeni-partiyi-h